Uses of Package
net.myorb.math.complexnumbers

  • Packages that use net.myorb.math.complexnumbers 
    Package Description
    net.myorb.math.complexnumbers
    Implementations of functionality supporting complex number fields.
    net.myorb.math.computational
    Support for computation in multiple dimensions mostly focused on calculus.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.charting
    Implementations of the charting interface that provide a default charting solution.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.charting.fractals
    Implementations of algorithms that compute plot data for fractals.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.controls
    Control layer for the CalcLib application including selection of the base type for a run.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.managers
    Implementation of the Space Management interface for the supported data types (Integer, Real, Complex).
    net.myorb.math.specialfunctions
    Implementations of algorithms supporting special functions (Bessel, Gamma, Ei, other).
    net.myorb.testing
    Implementations of algorithms supporting CalcLib unit tests.
